margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">中国古典园林史</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">中西方建筑文化交流</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">中国古代建筑史</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">文化遗产保护</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">【教育简历】</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1988-1992</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年，东南大学建筑系建筑学专业，获工学学士学位</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> </span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1995-1998</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年，北京建筑工程学院建筑系建筑设计及其理论专业，获建筑学硕士学位</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> </span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1998-2001</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年，清华大学建筑学院建筑历史与理论专业，获工学博士学位</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2001-2002</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年，法国华夏建筑学会短期访问学者</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2005-2006</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年，北京语言大学出国培训部意大利语班，获结业证书</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2006-2007</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年，意大利罗马大学建筑学院访问学者</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">【工作履历】</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1992</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">－</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">1995</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年，在江苏常州民用建筑设计院从事建筑设计工作</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> </span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2001-2004</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年，任清华大学建筑学院</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2004-2010</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年，任清华大学建筑学院</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2009</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年，取得博士生导师资格。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2010</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">年至今，任清华大学建筑学院</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><br></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">【学术兼职】</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2012</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span><span>6</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">月至今，中国圆明园学会理事、学术委员</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2012</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span><span>4</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">月至今，《中国建筑文化遗产》杂志社编委</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2011</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span><span>4</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">月至今，中国建筑学会史学分会理事、学术委员</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2008</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span><span>10</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">月至今，《古建园林技术》杂志社编委</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">【科研项目】</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">1以项目负责人的身份主持国家自然科学基金面上项目3项：</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> （1）《基于数字化技术平台的圆明园虚拟复原与造园意匠研究》（2013—2016，项目批准号51278264）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> （2）《中国北方地区私家园林研究与保护》（2012—2015，项目批准号51178233）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> （3）《北京私家园林历史源流、造园意匠及现代城市建设背景下的保护对策研究》（2007—2009，编号50678087）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> 2以项目负责人的身份主持清华大学基础研究基金1项：《明清北京私家园林造园艺术研究》（2003—2007，编号JC2003001）.</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"> 3先后主持和参与北京圆明园、北京故宫、西藏布达拉宫雪城、河南登封古建筑、山西太原晋祠、浙江东阳卢宅、浙江宁波保国寺、北京安徽会馆等20余项国家级重点文物建筑保护工程设计以及河南陈家沟古村复建、北京颐和园文物库馆、浙江绍兴宛委山与南镇庙风景区规划等建筑与规划工程设计。 &nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">【课程教学】</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">30020552</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《外国古代建筑史纲》：本科生理论课</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">80000421</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《中国古代建筑典籍文化》：研究生理论课</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">80000622</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《景观学史纲（亚洲部分）》：研究生理论课</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">40021194</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《建筑城市景观设计》：本科生设计课</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">40020342</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《古建筑测绘实习》：本科生实习课</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">80000484</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">《文物建筑保护规划及复原设计》：研究生设计课</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">【学术论著】</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">在学术期刊和国际学术会议上发表论文</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">90</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">余篇，独立完成并出版专著</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">部，参与编写出版专著</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">部（负责撰写其中相关章节），合作翻译出版英文专著</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">2</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">部，长期担任学术丛刊《建筑史》（原名《建筑史论文集》）主编。</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">代表性论著：</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1 </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">贾珺</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">北京私家园林志</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">北京清华大学出版社，</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2009</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2 </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">郭黛姮主编</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">远逝的辉煌—圆明园建筑园林研究与保护</span><span>. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">上海科技出版社</span><span>,2009</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（撰写</span><span>P1~5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">，</span><span>53~86</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">3 </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">王贵祥主编</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中国古代建筑基址规模研究</span><span>. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中国建筑工业出版社，</span><span>2008</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（撰写</span><span>P371~379</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">4 Musée Albert Kahn. Le Jardin du &nbsp;Lettre. Besançon: Les Éditions de L’Imprimeur, 2004, P170~187, Les &nbsp;jardin du Jiangnan dans l’art paysager à Pékin pendant les Ming et Qing</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span><span>[</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">法</span><span>]</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">阿尔伯·肯恩博物馆</span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">编</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">文人园林，负责撰写</span><span>P170~187</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">，“明清时期江南造园艺术对北京园林的影响”）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">5 </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">贾珺</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">山林凤阙—清代离宫朝寝空间及其场所特性</span><span>. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">建筑师</span><span>. 103</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">期</span><span>.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中国建工出版社，</span><span>2003</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：</span><span>74</span><span>~</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">81</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">6 </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">贾珺</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">山西万荣李家大院</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">古建园林技术</span><span>. 2006</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）：</span><span>52</span><span>~</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">56</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">7 </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">贾珺</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">北京私家园林社会文化内涵探析</span><span>. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">建筑学报</span><span>. &nbsp;2008</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span><span>1</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）：</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">103~106</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">8 </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">贾珺</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">三城鼎峙，署宇秩立—明代淮安府城及其主要建筑空间探析</span><span>. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">中国建筑史论汇刊，第</span><span>4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">辑</span><span>. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">北京：清华大学出版社，</span><span>2011</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">：：</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">255-280</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">9 </span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">贾珺</span><span>. </span> <span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">清代皇家园林写仿现象探析</span><span>. </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">装饰，</span><span>2010</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）：</span></span><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">16~21</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;font-weight: 700\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">【科研获奖】</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">1 2010</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span><span>4</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">月，专著《北京私家园林志》获第</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">届中国建筑图书奖之最佳史学图书奖（中国建筑学会建筑师分会、中国图书馆学会等</span><span>5</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"font-size:12px\">家单位联合颁发）</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 24px;margin-top: 2px;margin-bottom: 2px\"><span><span style=\"font-size:12px\">2 2009</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span><span>11</span></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><span style=\"f